  "description": "OSE OTel Demo workshop dashboard. Top row = always-visible projector strip (Tempo traces, service graph, RED metrics, Loki logs filtered by trace_id). Bottom row = collapsed deeper-dive (per-priority orders, error spans, raw logs).",
